インタフェース Villager

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    Ageable, Attributable, CommandSender, Creature, Damageable, Entity, InventoryHolder, LivingEntity, Metadatable, NPC, Permissible, ProjectileSource, ServerOperator

    public interface Villager
extends Ageable, NPC, InventoryHolder
    Represents a villager NPC

      • getProfession

        Villager.Profession getProfession()
        Gets the current profession of this villager.
        戻り値:

      • setProfession

      • getRecipes

        List<MerchantRecipe> getRecipes()
        Get a list of trades currently available from this villager.
        戻り値:
        an immutable list of trades

      • setRecipes

        void setRecipes(List<MerchantRecipe> recipes)
        Set the list of trades currently available from this villager.
        This will not change the selected trades of players currently trading with this villager.
        パラメータ:
        recipes - a list of recipes

      • getRecipe

                  throws IndexOutOfBoundsException

        戻り値:
        the recipe

      • getRecipeCount

        int getRecipeCount()
        Get the number of trades this villager currently has available.

        the recipe count

      • getInventory

        Inventory getInventory()
        Gets this villager's inventory.
        Note that this inventory is not the Merchant inventory, rather, it is the items that a villager might have collected (from harvesting crops, etc.) Get the object's inventory.
        定義:
        getInventory インタフェース内 InventoryHolder
        戻り値:
        The inventory.

      • isTrading

        boolean isTrading()
        Gets whether this villager is currently trading.
        戻り値:
        whether the villager is trading

        HumanEntity getTrader()

        戻り値:
        the trader, or null
